    <thetext>When all segments (hunks, files or folders) has been excluded from a patch the Finish should be disabled. At this moment, when the user excludes all the segments and clicks Finish, nothing will happen (the same result as clicking Cancel).

The Finish button in the case above should be disabled, additionally we could provide the user with a warning message at the top of the dialog.</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
