    <comment_count>1</comment_count>
    <who name="Tomasz Zarna">tomasz.zarna</who>
    <bug_when>2008-01-14 10:12:47 -0500</bug_when>
    <thetext>Also, we can&apos;t forget about projects from the patch that don&apos;t exist in the workspace, we should treat them the same way as they were excluded. In other words, if there is at least one segment that is neither excluded nor marked as &quot;non-existing&quot;, the button should be enabled, in any other situation it should be disabled.</thetext>
